2.0.0 - 2014-05-01

 * String.toNumber() now returns null instead of NaN
 * String.toNumber() accept the same options of String.isNumeric()
 * Date.isTheNextDay() has been renamed to Date.isNextDay
 * Date.isThePreviousDay() has been renamed to Date.isPreviousDay()
 * Reviewed internal documentation
 * Refactoring to follow common naming and formatting rules
 * Refactored trim() to adhere with standards
 * Reset undefined to ensure that nobody modified it
 * Tests can be run either with 'make test' or 'npm test'
 * Added testling support in package.json
 * Removed chai.js dependencies
 * New documentation website at http://www.sideralis.org/valib/

1.0.0 - 2014-03-10 

 * First stable release
